{"tid":1949293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戳灰藍店 從你我做起","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T05:06:00.000Z","uid":33930,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"050935f94ac7d220fe37ecade41f8a464e54636b","tid":1949293,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ab3GXu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAb3GXu1.jpg&h=22f33617&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我地發起 &quot;告&quot; &quot;罷&quot; 藍店 Challenge <br />\n<br />\n&quot;告&quot; 藍店 Challenge <br />\n利用藍營力量有效打擊藍營實力<br />\n而且仲係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">零成本</span></strong></span><br />\nwhy not ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更甚仲要營造出一種 <br />\n依家係班<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶毒狗同你地藍營作對</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以分化之道還治分化之身</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢14日一定唔可以放過佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果一但成功 , 獎勵將係最高<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">25000元及6個月</span></span></strong>，但可透過定額<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2000元</span></span></strong>取代 , 拒絕服從或提供虛假資料者最高<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">10000元</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;罷&quot; 藍店 Challenge <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0hP6ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0hP6ok.jpg&h=d0150fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地同場發起 &quot;罷&quot; 藍店 Challenge <br />\n就係係大家各大日常生活GROUP入面玩上 #Hashtag<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩法例子 : <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6gtCBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6gtCBY.jpg&h=daaf4c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#罷藍challenge  -  太興罷食第185日</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#2 會為大家提供藍店資料  歡迎取閱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZdDfgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZdDfgF.jpg&h=28d96ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他可以參詳之前既PO<br />\n【四月最新行動】&quot;罷&quot;&amp;&quot;告&quot; 藍店 Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947919</a>"},{"pid":"2948424abf0bc4fe523bc7e05a9bff18eae95899","tid":1949293,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvQex8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvQex8M.jpg&h=d7ab5d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1p68G6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1p68G6.jpg&h=fb1c8ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTBA116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTBA116.jpg&h=d82a88d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF0KaVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF0KaVr.jpg&h=3cb7df5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aa9Gc8N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAa9Gc8N.jpg&h=bfb0ac1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuSc4fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuSc4fs.jpg&h=4762a1d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8gxjON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.